Sultry telly and radio presenter Pearl Modiadie has sent shock waves through the showbiz industry when she called off her traditional wedding to her fiance Nkululeko Buthelezi for the second time in less than two years. Modiadie was supposed to have got married to Buthelezi, a businessman, in Tembisa, east of Joburg, yesterday. Invitations had already been sent out, but the sassy entertainment star, who presents SABC1 show Zaziwa, cancelled the wedding after she allegedly clashed with Buthelezi over various issues in the build-up to their big day, sources say. TO READ THE FULL STORY GET A COPY OF TODAY'S SUNDAY WORLD AT YOUR NEAREST STORE